summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of GO FISH! AAA enhancements. All 8 new feature buttons are visible and functional. Successfully tested Fish Breeding Lab with breeding/evolve/history tabs, Skill Tree with 6 skill categories, Mini Games launcher with 4 game options, Weather Widget with detailed weather display, Daily Rewards with 30-day calendar, and Achievement System with 40+ achievements. PLAY button works correctly and leads to stage selection. Game flow is fully functional.

ui_bugs.issue: Some modal close buttons have overlay interception issues requiring force clicks
ui_bugs.workaround: ESC key or force clicks work as alternative

passed_tests: Main menu loads with all 8 AAA enhancement buttons visible
Fish Breeding Lab modal opens with Breed/Evolve/History tabs
Skill Tree modal opens with 6 skill categories (Casting, Reeling, Patience, Strength, Luck, Mastery)
Daily Login Rewards modal opens with 30-day calendar and streak system
Mini Games launcher opens with 4 games (Fish Memory, Timing Catch, Fish Quiz, Fish Sort)
Weather Widget modal opens with weather conditions and fishing modifiers
Achievement System modal opens with 40+ achievements across 6 categories
Aquarium View modal opens and displays properly
PLAY button functionality works and leads to stage selection
Stage selection screen loads and allows game start
All modals can be closed successfully
Game flow from menu to gameplay is functional
